@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US08

autonumber

actor "Green Space\nManager" as Employee
participant ":System" as System

activate Employee

    Employee -> System : Asks to assign one ore more vehicle to an entry in the Agenda
    activate System

        System --> Employee : Shows the entries from the Agenda
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : Selects the entry from the Agenda
    activate System

        System --> Employee : Shows the available Vehicles
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : Selects one or more from the available vehicles
    activate System

        System --> Employee : Shows selected data and requests confirmation
    deactivate System

    Employee -> System : Confirms data
    activate System

        System --> Employee : Shows operations success message
    deactivate System



@enduml